YouTube Downloader

YouTube Downloader is a software program that allows you to download videos

The program is easy to use, just specify the URL for the video you want 
to download and click the Ok button! It also allows you to convert downloaded 
videos for Ipod, Iphone, PSP, Cell Phone, Windows Media, XVid and MP3.

You can use YouTube Downloader to download the videos of your choice from
home, at the office or in school. Download YouTube Downloader now and 
get started downloading your favorite videos from YouTube.

* Download videos from YouTube, Google Video, MySpaceTV and many others

* Converts video for Ipod, Iphone, PSP, Cell Phone, Windows Media, XVid and MP3

* Plays videos downloaded in Flash
* Extremely easy to use

* 64 MB of RAM
